criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  healthy individuals;

          -  adherent to Mediterranean diet

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  known medical disease;

          -  known digestive disease symptoms;

          -  known family history of celiac disease (CD);

          -  wheat allergy;

          -  and use of prescription medications (including antibiotics or probiotics in the
             previous 2 months)
